casebody.data:
Luis A. BENITES, Appellant,
v.
David BARRERA III, Appellee. No. 3D18-0008 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. Opinion filed February 20, 2019 Luis A. Benites, in proper person. David Barrera III, in proper person. Before SALTER, SCALES and MILLER, JJ. PER CURIAM.

Affirmed. See Applegate v. Barnett Bank of Tallahassee , 377 So.2d 1150 , 1152 (Fla. 1980) (holding that, in the absence of an adequate record of the proceedings below, an appellate court must affirm the trial court's judgment).
